### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### Get One Product With Query
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/123?include=details

### Create Product
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Widget",
  "price": 19.99
}

### Update Product
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Widget v2",
  "price": 24.99
}

### Delete Product
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/products/123

### Check Correlation Header Round-Trip
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products
X-Correlation-Id: test-corr
